  return /cocktail bar|craft cocktails?|speakeasy|lounge|nightclub|night club|brewery|tap room|taproom|tiki bar|mezcal|whiskey bar|wine bar|beer garden|rooftop bar|dive bar|listening bar|discotheque/.test(cu)
